Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术即分析 分解及重组物质的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其并非万能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法无中生有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想获得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须支付同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此即炼金术的基本原则「等价交换」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术师亦有禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都不可破此禁忌
Comment: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于雷奥尔教主的传闻 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹之术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是可以凭空炼出花来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能只是变变戏法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说不定就是那个说不定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜之间摧毁库塞路库塞斯遗迹的天上石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被东之贤者封印的强大炼金药（Elixir）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名称虽然五花八门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了就是能强化炼金术的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个 说不定就能找回阿尔的身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 写详细点会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这次能找对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把爸爸的书房弄得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎么能在那里涂鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是涂鸦啦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…炼金术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸教的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人都不在怎么教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书上写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算写着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是坏事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 不愧是爸爸的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈可以去跟大家炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲会称赞我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此感到欣喜的我们 一头扎进了炼金术的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那一年夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲感染了流行病 去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好冷 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是爸爸回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人不是我们爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连妈妈的葬礼都不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}（特丽莎·艾尔利克）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈能复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 书上说不能炼成人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就当是我俩的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是为去世的人而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭得越多 那个世界的人就会越伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也因为爸妈经常出门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一寂寞就哭鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才没哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 谁信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白担心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我晚到家就没你晚饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 爱德也把牛奶喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝就一直是矮子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是矮子 一寸老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 你这小豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微型小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚁尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在学校看闲书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好听课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 在看什么书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和温莉无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太诈了 你们什么都瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭是炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 回见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过发明炖菜的人真伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了牛奶居然那么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蔬菜汤里放牛奶这种想法本身就够牛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家也需要这样转换思想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体炼成一定也需要这种创意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后 我们为了让母亲复活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查人体炼成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟随炼金术的老师磨练技艺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知过了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想再见到母亲的笑容」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想再和母亲一起幸福生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一心只有这个念头…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 35升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳素 20千克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氨 4升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石灰 1.5千克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磷 800克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐分 250克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝石 100克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硫磺 80克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氟 7.5克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁 5克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硅 3克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始写构筑公式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是 灵魂的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好像不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…反噬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我在干什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你们称作世界的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者真理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 不知天高地厚的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是大量的情报 直接涌进脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 头要裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被分解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头像要裂开一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我突然明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人体炼成理论并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再差一点就能找到我所追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体炼成的真理了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 再让我看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点过路费只能看这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过路费？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 过路费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说等价交换吗 炼·金·术·师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么能…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 快来人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我所要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 那是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是手还是脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏都成 尽管拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我唯一的弟弟啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你还在中央呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸终于可以回东方司令部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来希望你至少升个准将啊 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得倒轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你回去之前这个先给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于艾扎克·麦克杜格尔的最终报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还没送到你手里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新国的炼丹术？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我是完全不了解 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 艾尔利克兄弟现在如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是他们的监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让爱德成为国家炼金术师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要卖身给军队 总有一天会看到地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱他们早就看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 也不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 艾尔利克兄弟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵啦 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们这些当兵的干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去过你们家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们炼了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是相当震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是听说有优秀的炼金术师才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能进行人体炼成 虽然还不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能成功锁定灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有足够的资质成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有任务时必须以士兵身份为国家卖命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同时可以获得各种特权以及进行最高端的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 他们有可能找到恢复原本身体的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他浑身浴血来我这里求救后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了他们家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西…那东西根本不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术是用来制造那种怪物的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反对你的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想让他们再看到地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我莉莎吧 莉莎·霍克艾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎小姐有射杀过人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌军人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸妈妈都是被带去战场然后被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们又要把爱德和阿尔带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去不去是他们自己的选择啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是强迫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为你提供了可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进还是驻足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要一生背负绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是怀着希望向军队低头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做决定的是他们俩自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果前方有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了恢复原本身体 就应该向前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便前方充满泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎小姐为什么会成为军人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有要保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再见啦 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 温莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年的眼睛里没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得那眼中燃烧着火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术和复健需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概三年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会累到吐血的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 你再忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你恢复原来的身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 到时候哥哥的身体也要一起恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体已经完全恢复了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下面就看炼金术了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以来一次都没用过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 炼成我的灵魂之后再没用过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 完美完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你好厉害 都没有用炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟老师一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔应该也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不行呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有看到那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要乱变形我的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头就能变形了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可爱的机械控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可爱也好 机械控也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你恢复原来的身体之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定全力支持你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您莅临考试现场还真难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说来了个12岁的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算来看看 也好作为谈资
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是钢铁的义肢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为东部内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 伊修瓦尔确实是个大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 他是金·布拉德雷大总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带了画炼成阵的工具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是相当出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会发生这种暗杀要人事件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种考试方式应该重新规划一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究是井底之蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的考试要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an8\fs23}（哈 哈 哈 哈）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过年轻的小炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时拔的刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥考试没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德如果成了国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会离开这个村子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是国家资格的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是任命书和相关细则 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统赐的名字还真讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就是堂堂正正的军队走狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以大总统金·布拉德雷的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命汝 爱德华·艾尔利克为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐「钢」之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 国家炼金术师都有别称
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你要背负的称号就是…
